{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDAwMDkyNTM0", "number": 4672, "title": "Issue 4669: (Bugfix) Fix serialization in PositionImpl.", "bodyText": "Change log description\nFix io.pravega.client.stream.Position#toBytes to ensure serialization works if the offset is -1L.\nPurpose of the change\nFixes #4669\nWhat the code does\nThe older revision of the client does not support serialization/deserialization with -1L as an offset.\nThis PR uses io.pravega.common.io.serialization.RevisionDataOutput#writeCompactSignedLong instead of io.pravega.common.io.serialization.RevisionDataOutput#writeCompactLong tofix the issue.\nBoth forward and backward compatibility is maintained with this change.\nHow to verify it\nAll the existing and newly added tests should continue to pass.", "createdAt": "2020-04-07T07:34:48Z", "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/pull/4672", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "a525aabd22f99b18f0df2df439eea9a9ee0da02d"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-04-16T05:39:54Z", "author": {"login": "shrids"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 14, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcVOOe_gH2gAyNDAwMDkyNTM0OjNkZDM0NDNjYTZlNDQ1YWMzMTViOWEzYmQ2NWI3M2M3ODUwOGUyMzE=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcX7FlFAFqTM5Mzk2MTU5MA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "3dd3443ca6e445ac315b9a3bd65b73c78508e231", "author": {"user": {"login": "shrids", "name": "Sandeep"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/commit/3dd3443ca6e445ac315b9a3bd65b73c78508e231", "committedDate": "2020-04-07T07:32:59Z", "message": "Fix by using compactSignedLong.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sandeep <sandeep.shridhar@emc.com>"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "3b6ef25359c60698811bc00c985c319c15d29b64", "author": {"user": {"login": "shrids", "name": "Sandeep"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/commit/3b6ef25359c60698811bc00c985c319c15d29b64",